6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to state government; enacting the
Statewide Official Compensation Commission Amendments
8 Act of 2026; providing for noncodification; and
providing an effective date.
9
10
11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
13 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
14 This act shall be known and may be cited as the "Statewide
15 Official Compensation Commission Amendments Act of 2026".
16 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
